<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79' lang=3Den-US>定義</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>自發性氣胸（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'>Spontaneous pneumothorax</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
      lang=3Dzh-TW>原發性（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;
      font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>Primary</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
      font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）：</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'
      lang=3Dzh-TW>無</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000;background:white' lang=3Dzh-TW>既</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000;
      background:white' lang=3Den-US>存</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000' lang=3Dzh-TW>肺病</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>的患者，常見於</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'
      lang=3Dzh-TW>年輕、瘦高、吸菸男性</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>繼發性（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Secondary </span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）：</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;
      color:#ED7D31'>因既存肺病引起的併發症</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>復發性氣胸（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Recurrent
      pneumothorax</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:11.0pt'>）：</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:11.0pt'>第二次氣胸發作，</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
      font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>不論是同側或對側</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>創傷性氣胸（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'>Traumatic pneumothorax</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>封閉性（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Closed</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>：空氣經由肺部的破洞進入（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;
      color:#ED7D31'>鈍傷</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
      font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>開放性（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Open</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>：胸壁全層破損，空氣經由胸壁的傷口進入，</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>肋膜腔與外界空氣自由連通</span></li>
  <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>又可為穿刺性（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>penetrating</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）或醫源性（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>iatrogenic</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>張力性氣胸（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'>Tension pneumothorax</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>胸腔內壓力持續升高，導致心肺功能受損（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>cardiorespiratory compromise</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>有生命危險</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>流行病學</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>原發性</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>男</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'> &gt; </span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>女</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>6</span><span
